<template>
    <v-snackbar
            v-model="$store.state.snackbar.display"
    >
        {{ $store.state.snackbar.text }}

        <template v-slot:action="{ attrs }">
            <v-btn
                    color="pink"
                    text
                    v-bind="attrs"
                    @click="$store.commit('displaySnackbar')"
            >
                Close
            </v-btn>
        </template>
    </v-snackbar>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    name: "Snackbar"
  }
</script>
